value.0: This is the person to talk to about racing. He can set up races or tell you the top racers at this track.
This version of the combat suit offers more protection than the basic model. It is heavier overall and not quite as flexible, but many consider the tradeoff worthwhile.

There are a variety of different kinds of armor intended to defend against the harsh enviroments of space, deflect the impact of blaster bolts and protect versus all types of damage that can be found on a battlefield. These suits are usually built in with a personal shield generator.

A double of curved panels forms an air-tight door. The transparent panes are of utmost curious material, neither liquid nor solid, but as strong and resistant than any treated iron and steel known to man.
Camera, Security (180 Degree Panning, Wall Mounted)
